Package: open-lnk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xdg-utils
Description: Open Windows .lnk shortcuts on Linux/macOS
 A small tool that parses Windows .lnk shortcut files, resolves targets to local
 paths or SMB URIs, and opens them with the system default handler.
